<title>
IMT Valve Actuator Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A1406010">IMT Valve Actuator Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
The IMT valve actuator may be damaged if battery voltage is applied to it for longer than 10 seconds.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Limit the time of battery voltage application to the IMT valve actuator to less than 10 seconds.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove IMT valve actuator. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1406010"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
